{"id":"concepts/web3-era","title":"Web3 era (Yahir, ~2021–2022)","type":"concepts","html":"<blockquote>\n<p>Stub. The <del>14-month stretch (</del>late 2021 → early 2023) where Yahir's vocabulary is dominated by <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/metaverse\">metaverse</a>, <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/coinbase\">coinbase</a>, DAOs, NFTs, and crypto-native product framing. Closes by 2023 — attention shifts fully to AI by 2024–2025.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2>Anchors</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2021-11-22-metaverse-land-thesis\">2021 11 22 metaverse land thesis</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2021-12-04-capitalisms-climate\">2021 12 04 capitalisms climate</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/corvallis-crypto-club\">corvallis crypto club</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/dao-mergers\">dao mergers</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/fweb3\">fweb3</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/ethereum\">ethereum</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/polygon-network\">polygon network</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/safemoon\">safemoon</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Connections</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/yahir-thesis-ai-search-2022-2026\">yahir thesis ai search 2022 2026</a> (the next era)</li>\n</ul>\n","related":[{"id":"summaries/2021-11-22-metaverse-land-thesis","label":"'Metaverse land most valuable around community' — Nov 2021 thesis"},{"id":"summaries/2021-12-04-capitalisms-climate","label":"Capitalism's Climate"},{"id":"entities/coinbase","label":"Coinbase"},{"id":"entities/corvallis-crypto-club","label":"Corvallis Crypto Club (CCC)"},{"id":"concepts/dao-mergers","label":"DAO Mergers"},{"id":"entities/ethereum","label":"Ethereum"},{"id":"entities/fweb3","label":"FWEB3"},{"id":"concepts/metaverse","label":"Metaverse"},{"id":"entities/polygon-network","label":"Polygon (Matic) Network"},{"id":"summaries/2023-04-12-questions-for-patrick-mooney","label":"Questions for Patrick Mooney — VC informational interview"},{"id":"entities/safemoon","label":"SafeMoon"},{"id":"concepts/yahir-thesis-ai-search-2022-2026","label":"Yahir's Evolving Thesis on AI Search & Distribution (2022–2026)"}]}
